<h1>OUR DIRECTOR</h1>
</div>
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
 <h4> <img src="images/chris.jpg" alt="chris" align="right" height="400" width="500" style= "PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px;"> &nbsp;
The current director of the Tidewater Concert band, Maestro Chris Serano.He has overseen TCB for over 6 years. Mr. Serano has been a professional percussionist for over 30 years.<p>
Mr. Serano is the percussion intstructer in residence and Russel's Music World. He is also a prolific performer and works as the permanent drummer for the award winning blue band Billy Joe Trio. <p>
 In addtion to performing and teaching, he manages a local booking agency, and is the founder and manager annual Virginia Drum show.</h4>
 


